{"tid":1715394,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解冇人整漆彈?","createTime":"2019-11-13T05:37:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T11:03:10.000Z","uid":110501,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"9bbcba30829e8e57a2913d9eaa4d1449b2973dbb","tid":1715394,"uid":110501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T05:37:10.000Z","msg":"漆彈呢樣野講左好耐 但係到而家都唔係好見 <br />\n而家我地有個問題係太focus於火魔法<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">只有一種武器 對家一有對策我地就好快輸</span></span> <br />\n一定要有多幾種武器<br />\n其實漆彈呢樣野對付狗車同狗都好有用<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong>1. 阻擋視野<br />\n加少少面粉之類既野加粘性 等佢難清 呢樣野係對車同人都有用 set rb果陣準備定幾個 有狗車想衝果陣掉佢車頭玻璃 等佢衝完都要停 甚至搏佢炒車 <br />\n</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">2. 封豬咀<br />\n其實唔止漆油 仲有食油 顏料呢D野用黎封豬咀都好有用</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">因為可以迫班狗一係退 一係除罩 </span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>3. 有手足被狗咬果陣 你唔可以放火魔法 都可以放漆彈然後救人<br />\n岩岩ifc出面比狗拉人果度 其實咁少狗 有漆彈壓制要救人會易好多</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n最重要既係 漆彈同火魔法比好低殺傷力 比D和理非或者有心理關口既人用"},{"pid":"e76214ae0e72630711366af5b5e34275acb857be","tid":1715394,"uid":337761,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T05:37:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">連登冷氣軍師 rt like reply</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">你哋已經唔使上前線搏命，係咪連呢啲都做唔到？</span><br />\n最新<br />\n<br />\n！！！！Sen. Cory Gardner (Colorado)<br />\n關注中大 支持香港<br />\n！！！！佢未cosponsor條Act 請佢幫忙！！！！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenCoryGardner/status/1194341990655246346?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenCoryGardner%2Fstatus%2F1194341990655246346%3Fs%3D19&d=lZ7jQHZQyV3jEURUmMbLafo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=d844b9fe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenCoryGardner%2Fstatus%2F1194341990655246346%3Fs%3D19&h=c0f128d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Se